OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1775851553
OL,3,CHow the Artemis crew will splash down
OL,4,Con Earth
OL,6,FWatch ITV News' Lucrezia Millarini
OL,7,Finterview the British astronaut Tim
OL,8,FPeake, as the Artemis II astronauts
OL,9,Fbegin their long journey home
OL,11,FThe final and most difficult part of
OL,12,Fthe Aretmis II voyage will take place
OL,13,Ftonight, with the crew navigating the
OL,14,Fdangers of re-entering the atmosphere
OL,15,Fbefore they splash down back on Earth.
OL,17,FAfter 10 days, the four crew members
OL,18,Fwill return from their journey, which
OL,19,Fhas seen them travel the furthest
OL,20,Fdistance from Earth any human ever has
OL,21,Fbefore.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
