PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1775851553
OL,3,CHow the Artemis crew will splash down
OL,4,Con Earth
OL,6,FSpeaking on Wednesday, pilot Victor
OL,7,FGlover said he'd been thinking about
OL,8,Fthe difficulty of re-entry since the
OL,9,Fday he was assigned to the mission on
OL,10,FApril 3 2023.
OL,12,FHere is how and when the Artemis crew
OL,13,Fwill return to Earth.
OL,15,FHow will the crew return to Earth?
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
