PN,31304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1775851553
OL,3,CHow the Artemis crew will splash down
OL,4,Con Earth
OL,6,FHours before the crew splash down,
OL,7,Fthey will begin by doing all the final
OL,8,Fpreparations required, including
OL,9,Fstowing all the equipment away and
OL,10,Fcalculating any final corrections they
OL,11,Fwill need to make to keep on course.
OL,13,FThey will then don their special Orion
OL,14,FCrew Survival System (OCSS) space
OL,15,Fsuits required for reentry.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
