PN,31305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1775851553
OL,3,CHow the Artemis crew will splash down
OL,4,Con Earth
OL,6,FThe bright orange suits are designed
OL,7,Fto keep astronauts alive for up to six
OL,8,Fdays if Orion loses cabin pressure,
OL,9,Fand include survival gear in case the
OL,10,Fcrew has to get out of Orion after
OL,11,Flanding in the ocean before recovery
OL,12,Fteams arrive.
OL,14,FThe service module will separate from
OL,15,FOrion 42 minutes before splashdown `
OL,16,Fleaving only the command capsule.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
